1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[English subtitles are available]

2
00:01:31,350 --> 00:01:36,060
[A Lonely Hero's Journey]

3
00:01:36,270 --> 00:01:38,729
[Episode 32]

4
00:01:52,950 --> 00:01:55,470
Miss Lu, have some tea and eat something.

5
00:02:02,030 --> 00:02:02,960
Go away.

6
00:02:03,350 --> 00:02:04,530
Have a seat.

7
00:02:16,910 --> 00:02:17,910
Where is this?

8
00:02:22,230 --> 00:02:23,230
You can't tell me?

9
00:02:28,270 --> 00:02:30,060
Did Ms. Lyuzhu use to live here?

10
00:02:30,570 --> 00:02:31,550
How did you know?

11
00:02:32,270 --> 00:02:33,910
A typical lady's bedroom

12
00:02:34,140 --> 00:02:36,020
wouldn't have opera costumes.

13
00:02:40,430 --> 00:02:42,360
Why is Ms. Lyuzhu not here anymore?

14
00:02:42,990 --> 00:02:44,160
I don't know.

15
00:02:44,310 --> 00:02:46,350
I'm just in charge of taking care of you.

16
00:02:46,350 --> 00:02:48,230
If you want to eat or drink anything,

17
00:02:48,230 --> 00:02:49,160
just let me know.

18
00:03:00,120 --> 00:03:01,140
Did I burn you?

19
00:03:02,230 --> 00:03:04,110
As servants, we have tough skin.

20
00:03:04,130 --> 00:03:06,130
We're not afraid of getting burned.

21
00:03:07,710 --> 00:03:09,240
How should I address you?

22
00:03:09,670 --> 00:03:10,670
My surname is Liu.

23
00:03:10,710 --> 00:03:12,440
You can call me Aunt Liu.

24
00:03:13,030 --> 00:03:14,710
Thank you, Aunt Liu.

25
00:03:16,010 --> 00:03:17,090
Hello, Mr. Luo.

26
00:03:17,710 --> 00:03:19,230
We found Miss Lu.

27
00:03:19,800 --> 00:03:20,670
She's fine.

28
00:03:20,880 --> 00:03:21,910
She's in Suzhou.

29
00:03:22,350 --> 00:03:23,680
She's absolutely safe.

30
00:03:24,870 --> 00:03:25,680
Mr. Li,

31
00:03:27,030 --> 00:03:30,250
I just want my governess to get back to Changshu

32
00:03:30,350 --> 00:03:33,030
as soon as possible.

33
00:03:33,870 --> 00:03:36,110
My children keep pestering me

34
00:03:36,130 --> 00:03:37,500
and throwing tantrums.

35
00:03:37,870 --> 00:03:39,910
They want to see Ms. Lu.

36
00:03:40,750 --> 00:03:42,000
No problem.

37
00:03:43,210 --> 00:03:45,730
I want to invite you

38
00:03:45,990 --> 00:03:47,310
back to Suzhou again

39
00:03:47,750 --> 00:03:50,270
to clear some misunderstandings.

40
00:03:53,710 --> 00:03:55,790
I dare not go to Suzhou.

41
00:03:55,870 --> 00:03:57,230
I bet

42
00:03:57,810 --> 00:03:59,270
you already know about it.

43
00:04:00,210 --> 00:04:02,080
The Japanese killed

44
00:04:02,150 --> 00:04:03,830
67 of my men.

45
00:04:05,670 --> 00:04:06,530
How about this?

46
00:04:07,110 --> 00:04:09,110
You can choose Shanghai or Nanjing.

47
00:04:09,390 --> 00:04:11,790
I'll personally pick you up from Changshu.

48
00:04:14,030 --> 00:04:15,530
There's more good news.

49
00:04:16,310 --> 00:04:17,810
Chairman Wang has agreed

50
00:04:18,230 --> 00:04:19,990
to all your requests.

51
00:04:20,829 --> 00:04:24,150
Money and guns are no longer a problem.

52
00:04:24,160 --> 00:04:25,620
You're getting off topic.

53
00:04:27,150 --> 00:04:28,010
How about this?

54
00:04:28,040 --> 00:04:31,040
I'll send someone to bring Ms. Lyuzhu

55
00:04:31,260 --> 00:04:33,830
back to Suzhou safely for you.

56
00:04:34,190 --> 00:04:37,430
You send someone to bring Ms. Lu

57
00:04:37,500 --> 00:04:39,550
back to Changshu safely.

58
00:04:39,550 --> 00:04:40,550
What do you think?

59
00:04:40,950 --> 00:04:42,230
Luo Wuqiang, listen.

60
00:04:44,110 --> 00:04:45,390
Ms. Lyuzhu

61
00:04:46,990 --> 00:04:49,950
doesn't deserve to be compared with Miss Lu.

62
00:04:50,960 --> 00:04:52,680
She sings Kun opera very well.

63
00:04:53,190 --> 00:04:56,400
Ask her to sing for you when you're free.

64
00:04:58,260 --> 00:04:59,070
I advise you

65
00:04:59,710 --> 00:05:03,270
to not trust the Communist Party.

66
00:05:04,330 --> 00:05:06,260
When we meet again,

67
00:05:07,110 --> 00:05:08,590
I'll definitely

68
00:05:09,790 --> 00:05:12,030
return Miss Lu to you in one piece.

69
00:05:14,660 --> 00:05:15,700
Think about it.

70
00:05:28,870 --> 00:05:30,640
Director Lin, you were right.

71
00:05:30,680 --> 00:05:31,340
Li

72
00:05:31,370 --> 00:05:32,750
is a despicable man.

73
00:05:33,350 --> 00:05:35,750
What? He still won't let her go?

74
00:05:37,040 --> 00:05:40,140
Commander, you must bear the consequences if you're indecisive.

75
00:05:40,140 --> 00:05:41,390
This is the best time for us to rebel

76
00:05:41,390 --> 00:05:42,790
and switch allegiances.

77
00:05:43,310 --> 00:05:44,710
If I can't save Lu Junnuo,

78
00:05:46,000 --> 00:05:47,600
I won't switch allegiances.

79
00:05:48,560 --> 00:05:51,060
Director Lin, what should we do next?

80
00:05:51,690 --> 00:05:52,950
Did the Suzhou squad for rescuing Xiao Ruotong

81
00:05:52,950 --> 00:05:54,990
report back yet?

82
00:05:55,000 --> 00:05:55,430
No.

83
00:05:55,909 --> 00:05:56,890
They found

84
00:05:56,990 --> 00:05:59,590
that Comrade Xiao is imprisoned in Villa No. 3.

85
00:05:59,710 --> 00:06:01,110
But it's heavily guarded.

86
00:06:01,110 --> 00:06:02,150
People from the agent headquarters,

87
00:06:02,150 --> 00:06:03,450
No. 76, are in charge.

88
00:06:03,510 --> 00:06:06,640
I also heard that Zhou Zhifei is guarding it personally.

89
00:06:06,800 --> 00:06:07,430
It's hard.

90
00:06:11,310 --> 00:06:12,170
How about this?

91
00:06:12,480 --> 00:06:13,880
Save Comrade Xiao first.

92
00:06:14,190 --> 00:06:15,770
We can't stop urging Luo Wuqiang

93
00:06:15,770 --> 00:06:17,370
to start an uprising either.

94
00:06:37,010 --> 00:06:40,470
[Wuqiang]

95
00:06:47,820 --> 00:06:47,920
[Wuqiang]

96
00:06:51,070 --> 00:06:51,940
I told you.

97
00:06:52,080 --> 00:06:53,250
Stay outside.

98
00:06:53,310 --> 00:06:54,330
You can't come inside.

99
00:06:54,330 --> 00:06:55,730
They can't come in.

100
00:06:55,770 --> 00:06:56,430
Not me.

101
00:06:57,190 --> 00:06:58,430
I'm here to serve you.

102
00:06:59,440 --> 00:07:00,170
[Principles of Chinese Economices]

103
00:07:29,310 --> 00:07:31,500
Yizhong, Ms. Wu is looking for you.

104
00:07:34,780 --> 00:07:36,980
You two talk. I'll go check on Junsheng.

105
00:07:40,590 --> 00:07:41,110
Sit.

106
00:07:45,350 --> 00:07:46,210
I remember you.

107
00:07:46,750 --> 00:07:47,830
Your husband

108
00:07:47,870 --> 00:07:50,400
died while escorting us to Chongshan Island.

109
00:07:50,590 --> 00:07:51,670
What’s the matter?

110
00:07:52,970 --> 00:07:54,230
Ruotong was captured.

111
00:07:55,770 --> 00:07:57,040
Don't worry.

112
00:07:57,430 --> 00:07:59,110
I know everything about you.

113
00:07:59,130 --> 00:08:00,590
I've been looking for her.

114
00:08:01,470 --> 00:08:02,330
Where did she go?

115
00:08:02,330 --> 00:08:03,190
Who caught her?

116
00:08:03,230 --> 00:08:04,360
Someone from No. 76.

117
00:08:04,870 --> 00:08:06,400
She's locked in Villa No. 3.

118
00:08:07,500 --> 00:08:08,670
Villa No. 3.

119
00:08:09,870 --> 00:08:11,070
[Harmony Brings Prosperity]

120
00:08:11,490 --> 00:08:13,220
It's where Lyuzhu used to live.

121
00:08:13,220 --> 00:08:14,880
We've been trying to save her.

122
00:08:15,530 --> 00:08:17,370
The squad has arrived in Suzhou.

123
00:08:18,190 --> 00:08:19,450
If nothing else works,

124
00:08:19,790 --> 00:08:21,120
we prepare to use force.

125
00:08:21,210 --> 00:08:22,030
Wait for me.

126
00:08:36,250 --> 00:08:37,190
This Villa No. 3

127
00:08:37,190 --> 00:08:38,450
is actually a spy den.

128
00:08:39,549 --> 00:08:40,710
The house in front

129
00:08:40,740 --> 00:08:43,190
is the Suzhou Head Office of the Pacification Operation Committee.

130
00:08:43,190 --> 00:08:44,900
The house No. 5 on its right

131
00:08:45,030 --> 00:08:46,530
is the house of the traitor Wang Manyun.

132
00:08:46,530 --> 00:08:48,020
It's guarded 24 hours a day.

133
00:08:48,020 --> 00:08:49,940
There are two altitude points across from it,

134
00:08:49,940 --> 00:08:51,760
which have two mobile sentries on them.

135
00:08:51,760 --> 00:08:52,820
The guards up there

136
00:08:52,830 --> 00:08:53,730
are elites selected

137
00:08:53,730 --> 00:08:55,110
by agent headquarters No. 76.

138
00:08:55,110 --> 00:08:55,870
I heard

139
00:08:56,270 --> 00:08:58,470
there's also a team of Japanese Military Police next door.

140
00:08:58,470 --> 00:08:59,750
So, if you want to use force

141
00:08:59,750 --> 00:09:00,680
to save Ruotong,

142
00:09:01,310 --> 00:09:02,590
it'll have grave consequences.

143
00:09:02,590 --> 00:09:03,910
Can you contact her?

144
00:09:08,210 --> 00:09:09,130
Ms. Wu,

145
00:09:09,930 --> 00:09:10,900
go back first.

146
00:09:12,030 --> 00:09:13,670
The day Commander Luo agreed to revolt

147
00:09:13,670 --> 00:09:14,830
is three days later.

148
00:09:15,150 --> 00:09:16,820
Mr. Li took her hostage,

149
00:09:16,950 --> 00:09:18,680
so we're all a bit scared to act.

150
00:09:19,480 --> 00:09:21,050
Director Lin believes

151
00:09:21,090 --> 00:09:23,350
we should rescue her as soon as possible.

152
00:09:24,110 --> 00:09:24,930
Don't worry.

153
00:09:26,040 --> 00:09:27,100
I'll figure it out.

154
00:09:44,710 --> 00:09:46,110
Liu Xiujuan.

155
00:09:49,590 --> 00:09:51,420
The leader of

156
00:09:51,500 --> 00:09:53,770
the operations outer squad

157
00:09:54,510 --> 00:09:56,530
actually came to be my maid.

158
00:09:57,660 --> 00:09:59,700
Mr. Li really thinks highly of me.

159
00:09:59,720 --> 00:10:00,290
Ms. Liu.

160
00:10:11,830 --> 00:10:14,090
It seems what the tabloids said was true.

161
00:10:15,070 --> 00:10:16,030
Two years ago,

162
00:10:16,050 --> 00:10:17,490
Madam Li brought the other madams to attack

163
00:10:17,490 --> 00:10:19,090
the place a lover was hidden.

164
00:10:19,160 --> 00:10:20,560
Turns out, it was for you.

165
00:10:23,240 --> 00:10:25,690
Miss Lu, your intelligence work is great.

166
00:10:26,230 --> 00:10:28,310
I can only say that you were careless.

167
00:10:28,650 --> 00:10:31,470
Your picture was published in the newspaper before.

168
00:10:31,470 --> 00:10:32,930
It left a deep impression.

169
00:10:33,470 --> 00:10:34,430
But I didn’t expect

170
00:10:34,430 --> 00:10:36,290
you would be hiding in Suzhou now.

171
00:10:37,780 --> 00:10:38,910
Where is the letter?

172
00:10:38,910 --> 00:10:39,870
What letter?

173
00:10:39,910 --> 00:10:41,310
It's either for your superiors

174
00:10:41,310 --> 00:10:42,740
or Commander Luo.

175
00:10:43,150 --> 00:10:44,070
You wrote it,

176
00:10:44,240 --> 00:10:46,330
but I'm sure you haven't sent it out.

177
00:10:55,970 --> 00:10:57,900
I have something urgent to report.

178
00:11:04,390 --> 00:11:04,950
Sir,

179
00:11:05,590 --> 00:11:08,190
I have important information to report to you.

180
00:11:09,750 --> 00:11:11,710
Don't ruin my mood.

181
00:11:13,220 --> 00:11:14,190
I have a way

182
00:11:14,550 --> 00:11:15,920
to make Luo Wuqiang

183
00:11:16,110 --> 00:11:17,630
and his 8,000 men

184
00:11:17,670 --> 00:11:19,400
belong to the Japanese Empire.

185
00:11:23,340 --> 00:11:23,910
Tell me.

186
00:11:24,630 --> 00:11:26,090
It is said that Luo Wuqiang

187
00:11:26,670 --> 00:11:28,320
and his family's governess,

188
00:11:28,470 --> 00:11:30,120
Lu Junnuo, have a special relationship.

189
00:11:30,120 --> 00:11:31,440
As long as we have Lu,

190
00:11:31,630 --> 00:11:34,030
we'll have a chance to control Luo Wuqiang.

191
00:11:34,190 --> 00:11:37,710
Luo Wuqiang will sell out his country?

192
00:11:41,550 --> 00:11:45,070
Where is Lu Junnuo now?

193
00:11:45,470 --> 00:11:48,230
Lu Junnuo was detained by Mr. Li secretly.

194
00:11:48,550 --> 00:11:50,900
Now, Zhou Zhifei is guarding her.

195
00:11:52,510 --> 00:11:55,150
Zhou Zhifei kept it from me again.

196
00:11:55,830 --> 00:11:56,870
Mr. Li

197
00:11:56,990 --> 00:11:58,480
wants to build an army alone

198
00:11:58,480 --> 00:12:00,110
to fight against the Japanese Empire,

199
00:12:00,110 --> 00:12:01,880
sabotage the "pacification" operation,

200
00:12:01,880 --> 00:12:03,130
and build a third government

201
00:12:03,130 --> 00:12:05,330
in addition to the Nanjing Government.

202
00:12:05,790 --> 00:12:08,470
It is said that there is even a radio in his house

203
00:12:08,550 --> 00:12:10,080
and he contacts Chongqing.

204
00:12:11,450 --> 00:12:14,050
Lieutenant Colonel Haruki warned him before.

205
00:12:14,800 --> 00:12:16,910
The Chinese are never reliable.

206
00:12:17,110 --> 00:12:19,110
It's traitors who are not reliable.

207
00:12:20,310 --> 00:12:21,310
Also,

208
00:12:22,790 --> 00:12:24,390
after Ding Jiansheng's case,

209
00:12:24,390 --> 00:12:26,990
I've been investigating the military rice case.

210
00:12:26,990 --> 00:12:29,150
Zhou Zhifei used the Shengyoulong Trading Co.

211
00:12:29,150 --> 00:12:31,050
run by his brother-in-law Ji Yuping

212
00:12:31,050 --> 00:12:32,590
and resold military provisions seven times

213
00:12:32,590 --> 00:12:34,180
since the start of the "pacification" operation.

214
00:12:34,180 --> 00:12:35,750
He's sold more than 150 million kilograms of military rice

215
00:12:35,750 --> 00:12:37,280
and made over 20 million in profit.

216
00:12:37,280 --> 00:12:38,150
This caused

217
00:12:38,150 --> 00:12:39,870
the rice price of Jiangsu and Shanghai to skyrocket,

218
00:12:39,870 --> 00:12:40,590
which has greatly damaged

219
00:12:40,590 --> 00:12:42,790
the reputation of the Japanese Empire.

220
00:12:49,350 --> 00:12:52,230
Zhou Zhifei is evil.

221
00:12:53,790 --> 00:12:54,590
That's right.

222
00:12:55,840 --> 00:12:57,640
Because he has Mr. Li behind him.

223
00:12:58,230 --> 00:12:59,550
I need to call Li

224
00:13:00,470 --> 00:13:02,470
and ask him to give us Lu.

225
00:13:02,620 --> 00:13:03,270
No.

226
00:13:04,390 --> 00:13:05,030
Sir,

227
00:13:05,750 --> 00:13:07,100
Mr. Li will deny

228
00:13:07,270 --> 00:13:09,070
that Lu Junnuo is in their hands.

229
00:13:09,230 --> 00:13:10,490
If we push him too hard,

230
00:13:10,670 --> 00:13:12,130
he might kill her instead.

231
00:13:14,430 --> 00:13:16,800
Have you forgotten the case of Jiang Boxian in 1941?

232
00:13:16,800 --> 00:13:18,230
In the end, Jiang Boxian went missing.

233
00:13:18,230 --> 00:13:19,200
Even his body went missing.

234
00:13:19,200 --> 00:13:20,550
It's all their doing.

235
00:13:22,070 --> 00:13:26,350
Gu, what do you think?

236
00:13:26,450 --> 00:13:28,310
I don't think we should hesitate.

237
00:13:28,750 --> 00:13:30,440
As long as we get Lu Junnuo

238
00:13:30,510 --> 00:13:31,910
from Mr. Li immediately,

239
00:13:32,630 --> 00:13:34,160
we'll have the initiative.

240
00:13:35,120 --> 00:13:36,880
Do you know

241
00:13:37,390 --> 00:13:38,430
where Lu Junnuo is?

242
00:13:38,430 --> 00:13:39,180
I have a spy.

243
00:13:39,830 --> 00:13:42,190
Sir, please send

244
00:13:42,210 --> 00:13:43,740
Sergeant Iwai to assist me.

245
00:13:44,230 --> 00:13:45,710
I will try to bring her back

246
00:13:46,470 --> 00:13:47,470
within one hour.

247
00:13:48,280 --> 00:13:49,140
How about this?

248
00:13:49,730 --> 00:13:52,030
You'd better not lie to me

249
00:13:52,030 --> 00:13:53,870
like Zhou Zhifei and Huang Xinzhai did.

250
00:13:53,870 --> 00:13:55,530
Otherwise, I will send troops

251
00:13:55,790 --> 00:13:57,150
to kill your wife Haimo

252
00:13:57,150 --> 00:13:58,440
and that child.

253
00:13:58,670 --> 00:14:01,110
I will burn Gu's Garden down!

254
00:14:01,910 --> 00:14:02,970
Do you understand?

255
00:14:04,850 --> 00:14:05,660
Yes.

256
00:14:12,750 --> 00:14:16,890
[To Commander Luo Wuqiang]

257
00:14:26,470 --> 00:14:31,080
[Harmony Brings Prosperity]

258
00:14:42,930 --> 00:14:43,720
Wake up.

259
00:14:43,750 --> 00:14:44,510
Wake up.

260
00:14:44,810 --> 00:14:46,300
Guard the door.

261
00:15:08,310 --> 00:15:09,070
Gu Yizhong.

262
00:15:11,070 --> 00:15:12,200
What can I do for you?

263
00:15:13,820 --> 00:15:14,680
Director Zhou.

264
00:15:15,430 --> 00:15:16,490
Where is Lu Junnuo?

265
00:15:30,710 --> 00:15:32,060
Why should I tell you?

266
00:15:33,730 --> 00:15:36,180
Mr. Kondo orders you to give Lu Junnuo

267
00:15:36,510 --> 00:15:37,350
to us.

268
00:15:49,960 --> 00:15:51,330
You're amazing.

269
00:15:52,830 --> 00:15:55,220
Even the Japanese have to listen to you.

270
00:15:59,830 --> 00:16:00,560
Go upstairs.

271
00:16:02,770 --> 00:16:03,820
Look upstairs.

272
00:16:18,520 --> 00:16:20,620
What are you doing?

273
00:16:20,800 --> 00:16:21,800
Vice Director Gu,

274
00:16:21,980 --> 00:16:23,400
what are you doing?

275
00:16:24,070 --> 00:16:24,530
This...

276
00:16:28,470 --> 00:16:29,470
Vice Director Gu.

277
00:16:29,860 --> 00:16:30,860
Vice Director Gu.

278
00:16:31,230 --> 00:16:32,070
What are you doing?

279
00:16:32,070 --> 00:16:32,730
Don't move.

280
00:16:33,840 --> 00:16:35,100
We're on the same side.

281
00:16:39,170 --> 00:16:41,250
Miss Lu, please come with us.

282
00:16:45,830 --> 00:16:46,770
Vice Director Gu,

283
00:16:46,770 --> 00:16:48,290
what happened?

284
00:16:49,500 --> 00:16:50,640
Miss Lu,

285
00:16:50,660 --> 00:16:52,020
