Zhou Zhifei's brother-in-law is a coward.

576
00:35:03,710 --> 00:35:06,670
He confessed without a fight.

577
00:35:07,190 --> 00:35:10,830
He admitted that he sold military provisions,

578
00:35:10,850 --> 00:35:13,250
not only rice but also cotton and medicine,

579
00:35:13,780 --> 00:35:18,350
but he denied the matter with the pass.

580
00:35:20,120 --> 00:35:20,870
Secretly

581
00:35:21,510 --> 00:35:23,490
arrest Zhou Zhifei.

582
00:35:26,880 --> 00:35:27,310
Yes.

583
00:36:19,360 --> 00:36:20,490
Take the valuable things.

584
00:36:20,490 --> 00:36:21,310
Okay.

585
00:38:42,200 --> 00:38:44,420
Mr. Kondo,

586
00:38:44,950 --> 00:38:45,970
I'm innocent!

587
00:38:46,340 --> 00:38:47,370
Please let me go.

588
00:38:48,110 --> 00:38:48,750
I have a lot of things—

589
00:38:48,750 --> 00:38:49,550
Go over there.

590
00:38:50,990 --> 00:38:51,740
Sit down.

591
00:39:02,620 --> 00:39:06,790
I heard you have something to tell me personally.

592
00:39:08,350 --> 00:39:09,160
Sir,

593
00:39:09,320 --> 00:39:11,110
we've been tricked.

594
00:39:11,670 --> 00:39:13,050
We fell into Gu Yizhong's trap.

595
00:39:13,050 --> 00:39:14,710
It's all a misunderstanding.

596
00:39:14,950 --> 00:39:17,550
You established a company with your brother-in-law

597
00:39:17,550 --> 00:39:19,410
and resold military provisions.

598
00:39:19,980 --> 00:39:22,340
You sold our military's rice

599
00:39:22,360 --> 00:39:24,020
to the New Fourth Army.

600
00:39:24,350 --> 00:39:27,180
This was also Gu Yizhong's trap?

601
00:39:27,220 --> 00:39:27,860
Iwai.

602
00:39:28,790 --> 00:39:30,200
In the Wang government,

603
00:39:30,220 --> 00:39:31,450
do you think I'm the only one

604
00:39:31,450 --> 00:39:32,780
reselling provisions?

605
00:39:33,000 --> 00:39:34,780
There are so many.

606
00:39:35,150 --> 00:39:37,360
Ji Yuping has confessed everything

607
00:39:38,110 --> 00:39:39,290
about how he got the rice

608
00:39:39,290 --> 00:39:40,740
and where he sold it to.

609
00:39:40,880 --> 00:39:42,070
It's clear.

610
00:39:42,830 --> 00:39:43,310
Yes.

611
00:39:43,710 --> 00:39:44,590
I plead guilty.

612
00:39:45,150 --> 00:39:47,150
I did sell military rice.

613
00:39:48,630 --> 00:39:49,390
Sir,

614
00:39:50,210 --> 00:39:51,880
please give me a chance.

615
00:39:52,670 --> 00:39:54,430
I want to make up for my mistake.

616
00:39:54,450 --> 00:39:55,090
Can I?

617
00:40:01,610 --> 00:40:02,970
I have an important

618
00:40:02,980 --> 00:40:04,540
military information

619
00:40:04,570 --> 00:40:05,850
to report to you.

620
00:40:06,750 --> 00:40:08,660
There's a senior agent

621
00:40:09,060 --> 00:40:10,780
from the communists

622
00:40:10,810 --> 00:40:13,350
who infiltrated the Suzhou Agent Station.

623
00:40:14,230 --> 00:40:15,900
His code name is Lonely Boat.

624
00:40:18,790 --> 00:40:19,550
Lonely Boat?

625
00:40:19,650 --> 00:40:20,230
Yes.

626
00:40:21,000 --> 00:40:21,790
Who is it?

627
00:40:22,310 --> 00:40:25,010
I only have a suspicion now,

628
00:40:25,670 --> 00:40:28,140
but I'm confident

629
00:40:28,230 --> 00:40:30,670
I can hand this person to you

630
00:40:30,690 --> 00:40:31,920
to punish,

631
00:40:32,510 --> 00:40:33,910
but I have one condition.

632
00:40:35,590 --> 00:40:38,140
If I can find Lonely Boat,

633
00:40:38,630 --> 00:40:40,990
I hope you can give me a chance.

634
00:40:41,950 --> 00:40:42,480
Of course.

635
00:40:42,480 --> 00:40:44,320
I can quit my job from No. 90.

636
00:40:44,680 --> 00:40:46,630
I just want to take my wife and child

637
00:40:46,650 --> 00:40:48,180
to farm in the countryside.

638
00:40:48,350 --> 00:40:50,070
Just give me a way out, okay?

639
00:40:54,790 --> 00:40:55,630
Yes.

640
00:40:55,960 --> 00:40:57,030
Thank you.

641
00:40:57,170 --> 00:40:59,230
I knew you'd say yes.

642
00:40:59,250 --> 00:41:00,090
Thank you.

643
00:41:02,630 --> 00:41:03,510
You two

644
00:41:04,130 --> 00:41:06,130
are very familiar with this person.

645
00:41:09,160 --> 00:41:10,530
Gu Yizhong.

646
00:41:12,300 --> 00:41:13,750
Don't doubt me.

647
00:41:13,790 --> 00:41:16,070
Do you remember Wang Mingzhong?

648
00:41:16,770 --> 00:41:18,190
A few days ago,

649
00:41:18,670 --> 00:41:20,010
Commander Luo Wuqiang

650
00:41:20,050 --> 00:41:21,580
came to our No. 90 to get him.

651
00:41:22,010 --> 00:41:24,860
Wang Mingzhong, the Communist liaison,

652
00:41:24,950 --> 00:41:26,230
later died in No. 90.

653
00:41:27,400 --> 00:41:29,510
He was Lonely Boat's superior.

654
00:41:30,420 --> 00:41:31,910
After he died,

655
00:41:31,940 --> 00:41:34,780
I found a book of poems on him.

656
00:41:34,990 --> 00:41:36,030
This book

657
00:41:36,050 --> 00:41:38,010
was the token used

658
00:41:38,110 --> 00:41:40,180
when he met with Lonely Boat in person.

659
00:41:40,180 --> 00:41:41,320
I have an idea.

660
00:41:41,670 --> 00:41:44,210
Let's get someone to call Gu Yizhong.

661
00:41:44,550 --> 00:41:46,050
Tell him the communists

662
00:41:47,230 --> 00:41:48,480
sent someone

663
00:41:48,510 --> 00:41:50,490
with a book of poems.

664
00:41:51,070 --> 00:41:52,430
I guess Gu Yizhong

665
00:41:52,450 --> 00:41:53,840
must have this book.

666
00:41:54,280 --> 00:41:55,810
Have him come for a liaison.

667
00:41:56,070 --> 00:41:58,250
Then, the truth will be revealed

668
00:41:58,590 --> 00:42:00,520
that Gu Yizhong is Lonely Boat

669
00:42:00,550 --> 00:42:02,340
and we'll catch them all.

670
00:42:02,790 --> 00:42:03,430
Iwai,

671
00:42:03,980 --> 00:42:05,250
this book of poems

672
00:42:05,750 --> 00:42:07,010
is in the second drawer

673
00:42:07,270 --> 00:42:08,510
of my office.

674
00:42:08,680 --> 00:42:09,490
Go get it.

675
00:42:10,190 --> 00:42:11,650
You'll know after trying.

676
00:42:16,690 --> 00:42:18,450
Okay, this is it.

677
00:42:20,350 --> 00:42:21,190
Slowly.

678
00:42:28,430 --> 00:42:29,390
You're so smart.

679
00:42:31,010 --> 00:42:31,600
Hello?

680
00:42:32,310 --> 00:42:34,550
Hello, is this Mr. Gu Yizhong?
